            {
                "title": "Individual Income Tax",
                "data": [
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "data": "The individual income tax ranges from 9% to 44%. Income tax is calculated according to progressive rates. Multiple additional factors may impact overall rates such as the household status and the number of children."
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "table",
                        "data": [
                            {
                                "Gross Annual Income": "Up to EUR 10,000",
                                "Tax Rate (%)": "9%"
                            },
                            {
